org.testah.driver.web.browser

Class AbstractBrowser<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.testah.driver.web.browser.AbstractBrowser<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type parameter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FirefoxBrowser, FirefoxGeckoBrowser, GoogleChromeBrowser, JBrowserDriverBrowser, PhantomJsBrowser

    public abstract class AbstractBrowser<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class AbstractBrowser wraps Webdriver Api implementation with many macrotized methods to reduce code in tests.
